A warm, nostalgic vintage photograph-style image of two identical candles shaped like the number 10, glowing softly on a birthday cake decorated with intricate frosting swirls. Beside the cake sits an unopened robotics construction kit with colorful mechanical pieces visible through clear packaging, and a mysterious board game with a maze pattern on its cover. The scene is bathed in golden afternoon light streaming through a window, casting long shadows across a wooden family dining table. Scattered confetti and curled ribbons in festive colors frame the composition. The mood is celebratory yet intimate, capturing a milestone moment of childhood wonder and parental joy.
